<div class="com-share" data-id="23399" data-title="《这家只点煤油灯的旅馆，很适合你厌世的时候躲一躲》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/23399/medium/23399.jpg?1457322142" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/23399.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
